1
00:00:46,740 --> 00:00:50,980
=The Antidote to Love=
=Episode 7=

2
00:01:39,360 --> 00:01:40,400
What are you doing?

3
00:01:40,820 --> 00:01:42,360
I'm treating your wound.

4
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:52,480
Sorry.

5
00:02:01,500 --> 00:02:02,580
Don't move.

6
00:02:05,340 --> 00:02:06,600
Let me tell you.

7
00:02:06,600 --> 00:02:08,280
This cut is pretty deep.

8
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:10,240
If you don't treat it soon,

9
00:02:11,040 --> 00:02:12,450
it could get infected.

10
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:14,110
Do you know that?

11
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:15,520
But

12
00:02:16,920 --> 00:02:18,190
you're in luck today.

13
00:02:18,200 --> 00:02:19,460
You happened to meet me.

14
00:02:31,340 --> 00:02:32,180
You...

15
00:02:32,180 --> 00:02:33,800
Hold this yourself.

16
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,520
I'll cook something for you.

17
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,570
The food's ready.

18
00:02:48,760 --> 00:02:50,080
Time to eat.

19
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:51,390
Get up and eat.

20
00:02:52,780 --> 00:02:53,620
Hello.

21
00:02:59,580 --> 00:03:00,500
Hey.

22
00:03:01,060 --> 00:03:02,420
Get up; it's time to eat.

23
00:03:03,740 --> 00:03:04,580
Hello.

24
00:03:09,660 --> 00:03:10,500
Hey.

25
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:12,060
Hey, wake up.

26
00:03:13,100 --> 00:03:13,940
Hey.

27
00:03:14,300 --> 00:03:15,940
Hey, don't die.

28
00:03:16,920 --> 00:03:17,760
What should I do?

29
00:03:19,540 --> 00:03:20,420
What can I do?

30
00:03:20,480 --> 00:03:21,650
Medicine...

31
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:04,190
You're awake.

32
00:04:06,160 --> 00:04:07,520
What are you doing?

33
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:10,880
Today is the Shangsi Festival
of the Moon Clan.

34
00:04:10,880 --> 00:04:11,850
Do you want to join us?

35
00:04:12,320 --> 00:04:13,160
The Shangsi Festival?

36
00:04:18,640 --> 00:04:19,520
Come with me.

37
00:04:42,050 --> 00:04:46,010
♪One day, the story unfolds♪

38
00:04:46,350 --> 00:04:50,950
♪The tale begins right here♪

39
00:04:51,570 --> 00:04:55,640
♪Later, I could only blame the rain♪

40
00:04:58,260 --> 00:04:59,460
What do you think?

41
00:05:00,850 --> 00:05:03,360
♪I can't solve the puzzle you left♪

42
00:05:04,760 --> 00:05:06,100
You look good.

43
00:05:08,180 --> 00:05:09,080
By the way,

44
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:11,260
what's the Shangsi Festival?

45
00:05:12,060 --> 00:05:13,980
Well, the festival

46
00:05:14,320 --> 00:05:16,360
means blessed rain from the sky,

47
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:18,060
and all things wake to life again.

48
00:05:18,060 --> 00:05:20,560
That's when we have someone

49
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:22,960
to share the warm breeze
and the idle days with.

50
00:05:23,520 --> 00:05:27,600
People gather and wander
through the night,

51
00:05:27,870 --> 00:05:30,880
drinking from the floating wine,
surrounded by willows,

52
00:05:30,940 --> 00:05:33,840
bathing by the river,
and dancing to the melody.

53
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:36,400
Together, we drive misfortune away

54
00:05:36,950 --> 00:05:38,650
and hope to find someone dear.

55
00:05:43,960 --> 00:05:45,040
What do you think?

56
00:05:49,130 --> 00:05:51,550
♪I can't solve the puzzle you left♪

57
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:52,960
You won't be disappointed.

58
00:05:53,970 --> 00:05:58,650
♪Being so far from you♪

59
00:05:58,830 --> 00:06:01,380
♪The ripples you stirred in my heart♪

60
00:06:01,380 --> 00:06:03,500
♪Would never fade♪

61
00:06:03,740 --> 00:06:07,910
♪I can't erase you from my soul♪

62
00:06:08,100 --> 00:06:13,030
♪I search for you in the misty rain♪

63
00:06:13,390 --> 00:06:17,510
♪Or by the ancient divine relic♪

64
00:06:17,710 --> 00:06:22,350
♪I follow the sound of the camel bell♪

65
00:06:22,520 --> 00:06:23,470
Young man,

66
00:06:23,470 --> 00:06:25,200
you truly are blessed with luck.

67
00:06:25,210 --> 00:06:26,080
If the Saintess

68
00:06:26,080 --> 00:06:28,400
hadn't saved you with her blood,

69
00:06:28,500 --> 00:06:30,040
you might not have made it till now.

70
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,500
I'll tell you a little secret.

71
00:06:32,500 --> 00:06:33,460
In the Moon Clan,

72
00:06:33,460 --> 00:06:35,420
there's a taboo passed down for ages.

73
00:06:35,940 --> 00:06:38,600
They say saving outsiders with her blood

74
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,880
will bring calamity to our clan.

75
00:06:40,880 --> 00:06:42,140
But I don't believe it.

76
00:06:43,790 --> 00:06:44,880
Come on, drink up.

77
00:06:45,620 --> 00:06:46,500
Here, have a drink.

78
00:06:47,340 --> 00:06:48,180
Come on.

79
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,600
What's this?

80
00:07:23,080 --> 00:07:25,640
It's our wishing coin.

81
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:27,080
It's quite effective. Try it.

82
00:07:44,020 --> 00:07:45,280
What did you wish for?

83
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,320
I wished

84
00:07:48,840 --> 00:07:50,260
to be with Yun Yao

85
00:07:50,260 --> 00:07:51,450
forever.

86
00:08:13,580 --> 00:08:15,660
(Two days later)

87
00:08:25,760 --> 00:08:26,960
Let's part ways here.

88
00:08:40,140 --> 00:08:41,820
Once Father agrees to our union,

89
00:08:42,760 --> 00:08:44,280
I'll return to marry you at once.

90
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:54,780
♪A small boat♪

91
00:08:54,780 --> 00:08:57,740
♪In the haze, your shadow drifts♪

92
00:08:58,090 --> 00:09:02,800
♪The mist afar hides someone's past♪

93
00:09:05,100 --> 00:09:07,930
♪Years slip by in silence♪

94
00:09:07,930 --> 00:09:09,480
♪The lone cliff has gone♪

95
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:10,520
I'll wait for you.

96
00:09:10,520 --> 00:09:12,030
♪Stories adrift in mountains and seas♪

97
00:09:12,030 --> 00:09:15,320
♪Appear in someone's dreams♪

98
00:09:17,380 --> 00:09:18,220
I'll wait for you.

99
00:09:19,310 --> 00:09:22,090
♪Alone, I greet the season
of falling blossoms♪

100
00:09:22,090 --> 00:09:23,520
♪Flowers change♪

101
