134
00:11:09,800 --> 00:11:13,520
♪Autumn wind stirs gentle ripples♪

135
00:11:13,520 --> 00:11:17,200
♪Before the flowers bloom
and fill the earth♪

136
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:23,160
